Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.95,0:55:36.85,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, why do these kinds of things always happen to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.05,0:55:39.70,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What are we going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.70,0:55:41.55,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What we always do!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.55,0:55:42.75,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Save the day!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.35,0:55:49.45,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh boy, oh boy, oh boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.45,0:55:51.00,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This is gonna be so much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.00,0:55:54.55,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh! I only wish we had time to make superhero capes!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.55,0:55:56.00,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.70,0:55:58.45,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Enough about our wardrobe!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.45,0:56:01.35,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We've got to stop Gloriosa from trapping everybody in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.90,0:56:21.15,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Um, hi
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.30,0:56:22.70,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Do you think you can give us a hand–
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.70,0:56:26.55,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Um, er, paw? We could really use a way out
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.65,0:57:32.85,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This isn't working!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.85,0:57:34.60,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Her magic is too strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.90,0:57:40.10,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Nice work, Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.25,0:57:47.25,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Twilight, you have to use your magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.45,0:57:49.85,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I don't think I can lift something that big
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.85,0:57:51.95,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's our only chance of getting out of here
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.95,0:57:53.30,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and helping our friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.00,0:58:20.35,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why are you fighting me?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.35,0:58:22.60,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm doing this to save our camp!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.60,0:58:24.55,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm doing this for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.60,0:58:29.70,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Gloriosa, let's just think about this for a moment, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.70,0:58:34.15,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I mean, I think Camp Everfree is absolutely delightful
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.15,0:58:38.50,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,but I just don't know that if I'm quite ready to give up my weekly trips to the spa.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.25,0:58:40.80,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,To the spa
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.30,0:58:43.85,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,TO THE SPA?!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.75,0:58:52.70,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Gloriosa, this isn't the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.70,0:58:55.40,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I appreciate your concern, Timber
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.40,0:58:57.30,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,BUT I GOT THIS!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.65,0:59:02.65,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No, you don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.70,0:59:12.45,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Twilight, do you think you can use your magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.25,0:59:14.75,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I don't wanna use too much
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.75,0:59:16.55,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Midnight Sparkle could take over
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.00,0:59:20.00,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Twilight, our friends are in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.55,0:59:24.45,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.55,0:59:31.95,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Please, Gloriosa
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.95,0:59:33.70,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What you're doing is crazy
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.70,0:59:35.45,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You have to listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.45,0:59:37.15,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That isn't Gloriosa
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.55,0:59:42.35,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.35,0:59:43.20,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sunset!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.20,0:59:44.25,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.65,0:59:46.00,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That isn't your sister
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.10,0:59:49.00,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's someone who's been consumed by Equestrian magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.90,0:59:53.90,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Whoever you are, you have to let my sister go!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.90,0:59:56.05,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Please, Gloriosa, come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.05,0:59:57.30,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I need you!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.00,1:00:01.35,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Gloriosa!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.75,1:00:14.65,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Rarity!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.95,1:00:21.50,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I can't keep this up forever!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.00,1:00:23.35,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's up to you
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.35,1:00:26.35,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You can use your magic to pull the brambles apart!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.35,1:00:28.45,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No. There's too many of them
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.45,1:00:31.20,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It would take too much magic. I can't!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.20,1:00:32.65,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's the only way!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.65,1:00:35.30,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You have to embrace the magic inside you!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.30,1:00:37.20,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What if she takes over?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.20,1:00:39.05,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What if instead of saving everyone
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.05,1:00:41.85,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I turn into Midnight Sparkle and only make things worse?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.85,1:00:43.65,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That won't happen!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.65,1:00:45.05,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We won't let it
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.00,1:00:56.10,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Come on, Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.10,1:00:58.45,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You have to be stronger than she is!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.95,1:01:10.95,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You will never control me! I will always be a part of you!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.90,1:01:16.50,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Nooo!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.10,1:01:21.30,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Twilight, listen to me! You are in charge!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.55,1:01:25.65,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You are a light, darling! A force for good!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.75,1:01:28.85,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah! You can kick the darkness's butt!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.05,1:01:31.15,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We're here for you, Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.35,1:01:33.50,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And we'll be here no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.70,1:01:35.90,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We believe in you!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.05,1:01:41.35,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You are not Midnight Sparkle!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.75,1:01:47.50,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,, No! I am Twilight Sparkle!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.70,1:01:52.75,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And the magic I carry inside me is... the Magic of Friendship!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.55,1:02:02.20,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.95,1:02:51.20,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Gloriosa?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.90,1:02:56.50,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What... What happened?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.70,1:02:57.60,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's okay
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.40,1:02:59.70,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's gonna be okay
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.95,1:03:11.05,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You did it!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.30,1:03:13.55,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, nice bling
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.00,1:03:16.20,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What... What are these?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.20,1:03:17.40,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.60,1:03:20.55,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But clearly we have some kind of connection to them
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.70,1:03:23.20,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I almost don't care what they are
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.35,1:03:25.10,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,They are gorgeous!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.50,1:03:29.55,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And will totally go with the other collection I was working on for the camp fashion show!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.15,1:03:35.20,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's probably cancelled, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.10,1:03:41.10,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,, I am so sorry
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.50,1:03:45.55,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I only wanted this to be the best week Camp Everfree has ever had
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.55,1:03:48.15,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Then instead I've made it the worst
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.75,1:03:51.90,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's for the best that I'm losing the camp to Filthy Rich
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.20,1:03:54.55,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No, it's not
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.55,1:03:57.55,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This camp has meant so much to so many people
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.55,1:03:59.55,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,my sister and me included
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.90,1:04:02.85,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why do you think we wanted our students to come here?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.25,1:04:06.15,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We can't let Filthy Rich take this place away!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.15,1:04:08.35,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If camp meant so much to you two
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.35,1:04:12.10,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,maybe it meant as much to the other campers who came here in years past
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.25,1:04:15.50,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And maybe we can get them to help save it!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.60,1:04:17.40,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh! Like a fundraiser?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.60,1:04:19.35,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Or a ball?!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.35,1:04:20.90,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Our band could play!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.90,1:04:23.75,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I can help writing a new song just for the occasion!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.10,1:04:31.60,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Those are all good ideas, but where would we hold it?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.60,1:04:33.65,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We can hold it in the crystal cave!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.75,1:04:38.10,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A Crystal Ball! I'm on it!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.30,1:04:40.75,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I admire everyone's enthusiasm
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.75,1:04:41.95,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Really, I do
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.95,1:04:45.20,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But I-I just don't know how we're going to plan a ball by tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.20,1:04:46.30,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and invite everyone
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.70,1:04:48.25,English Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We got this!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.95,0:55:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么这种事总是发生在我们身上啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.05,0:55:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我们现在该怎么办啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.70,0:55:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,干我们的老本行啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.55,0:55:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,拯救大家！
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.35,0:55:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,天哪，天哪，天哪！
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.45,0:55:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这一定会非常好玩的！
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.00,0:55:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我真希望我们能抽点儿时间去做几件超级英雄披风！
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.55,0:55:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,加我一个！
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.70,0:55:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,别再聊那些穿的东西了！
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.45,0:56:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还得阻止嘉兰把大家困在营地里呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.90,0:56:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,呃，嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.30,0:56:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你们能否帮我们一把…
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.70,0:56:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,呃，一爪？我们真的很需要一条能出去的路
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.65,0:57:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,没有用！
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.85,0:57:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,她的魔法太强大了！
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.90,0:57:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,干得好，斯派克！
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.25,0:57:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,暮光，你必须使用你的魔法！
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.45,0:57:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我不觉得我能搬得动这么大的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.85,0:57:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我们能帮助朋友们
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.95,0:57:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,并逃离这里的唯一可能啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.00,0:58:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,为何你们都要跟我作对？
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.35,0:58:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我可是在拯救我们营地啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.60,0:58:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我可是为了你们好！
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.60,0:58:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,嘉兰，我们来稍微讨论下这事如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.70,0:58:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说，森灵营地的确非常棒
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.15,0:58:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,但我不知道我是否准备好放弃享受我每周一次的水疗了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.25,0:58:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,享受水疗？
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.30,0:58:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,享受水疗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.75,0:58:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,嘉兰，没必要这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.70,0:58:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我很感谢你的关心，云杉
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.40,0:58:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我会搞定的！
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.65,0:59:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不，你没有！
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.70,0:59:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,暮光，你能使用你的魔法吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.25,0:59:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想使用过度
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.75,0:59:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,午夜闪闪可能会控制我
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.00,0:59:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,暮光，我们的朋友可都在里面啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.55,0:59:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.55,0:59:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,嘉兰，拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.95,0:59:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你的所作所为简直太疯狂了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.70,0:59:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定得听我说！
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.45,0:59:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是嘉兰
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.55,0:59:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,暮光！
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.35,0:59:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,余晖！
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.20,0:59:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧你们！
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.65,0:59:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是你姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.10,0:59:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那只是个被小马国魔法吞噬的人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.90,0:59:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不管你是谁，快把我姐姐还回来！
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.90,0:59:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托，嘉兰，快点回来！
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.05,0:59:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要你！
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.00,1:00:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,嘉兰！
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.75,1:00:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞瑞！
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.95,1:00:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我没办法永远挡住这些荆棘！
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.00,1:00:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,看你的了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.35,1:00:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以用你的魔法扯断这些荆棘！
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.35,1:00:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，太多了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.45,1:00:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我做不到！这会消耗太多魔法了！
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.20,1:00:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这是唯一的办法了！
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.65,1:00:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你得接纳你的魔法
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.30,1:00:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,万一她控制了我呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.20,1:00:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,万一我变成了午夜闪闪
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.05,1:00:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不仅没能救到我们反而让事情变得雪上加霜了呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.85,1:00:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那不会发生的！
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.65,1:00:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不会让它发生的
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.00,1:00:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧，暮光！
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.10,1:00:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你得要比她更强大！
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.95,1:01:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你永远无法掌控我！我永远是你的一部分！
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.90,1:01:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.10,1:01:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,暮光，听我说！你可以控制住的！
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.55,1:01:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你是一道光，亲爱的！你是正义的力量
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.75,1:01:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,对！你能赶走黑暗势力的！
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.05,1:01:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我们支持你，暮光！
Dialogue: 0,1:01:31.35,1:01:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我们无论如何都会在你身边
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.70,1:01:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我们相信你！
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.05,1:01:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是午夜闪闪！
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.75,1:01:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,没错！我是暮光闪闪！
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.70,1:01:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我心中的魔法就是友谊魔法！
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.55,1:02:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不！住手！
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.95,1:02:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,嘉兰？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.90,1:02:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,发…发生了什么事？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.70,1:02:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,没事了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.40,1:02:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.95,1:03:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你做到了！
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.30,1:03:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,喔，光泽不错
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.00,1:03:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这些...东西到底是啥？
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.20,1:03:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.60,1:03:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,但显然的我们跟这些东西有着某种联系
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.70,1:03:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我才不管这些东西是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.35,1:03:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,它们看起来超漂亮！
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.50,1:03:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,和我为了营地时装秀而做出的其他作品很搭
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.15,1:03:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不过时装秀应该已经被取消了，对吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.10,1:03:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.50,1:03:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想要让大家有个史上最棒的露营周
Dialogue: 0,1:03:45.55,1:03:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,结果我却搞砸了一切
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.75,1:03:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,或许让臭钱接手营地才是最好的选择
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.20,1:03:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不，并不是
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.55,1:03:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这营地对很多人来说都很重要
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.55,1:03:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,包括了我和我的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.90,1:04:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不然你认为我们为什么会选择带我们的学生来到这里
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.25,1:04:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不能让臭钱夺走这座营地！
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.15,1:04:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,如果这营地对你们姐弟俩很重要
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.35,1:04:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,或许也对历年以来在这里露营的其他营员们一样重要
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.25,1:04:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我们能让他们帮忙一起来拯救营地！
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.60,1:04:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，像是办场募捐活动？
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.60,1:04:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,或是办场舞会？
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.35,1:04:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我们乐队可以表演！
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.90,1:04:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以帮忙专门写首新歌！
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.10,1:04:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这些的确都是好主意，但我们该在哪里举办？
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.60,1:04:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以办在水晶洞穴里！
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.75,1:04:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,一场水晶舞会！我这就去办！
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.30,1:04:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我很感谢大家的热情相助
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.75,1:04:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.95,1:04:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,但我-我不知道要怎么才能赶在明天前筹备好一场舞会
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.20,1:04:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,并邀请大家都来参加
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.70,1:04:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会搞定的！
